      <nav>
        <a href="/fastigheter-till-salu/">Till salu</a>
        <a href="/salja-bostad/">Sälja</a>
        <a href="/kopa-bostad/">Köpa</a>
        <a href="/om-oss/">Om oss</a>
        <a href="/kontakta-oss/" class="active">Kontakt</a>
      </nav>

      <a href="/vardering-av-bostad/" class="btn btn-primary">Boka värdering</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <h1>Kontakta oss</h1>
      <p>Kontakta oss idag för en smidigare bostadsförsäljning</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-form">
        <h2>Har du frågor?</h2>
        <p>Fyll i formuläret nedan så tar en av våra representanter kontakt med dig inom 24h.</p>

        <form>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="firstname">Förnamn *</label>
              <input type="text" id="firstname" name="firstname" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="lastname">Efternamn *</label>
              <input type="text" id="lastname" name="lastname" required>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="company">Företag</label>
            <input type="text" id="company" name="company">
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">E-post *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Telefon</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Meddelande</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="checkbox-group">
            <input type="checkbox" id="gdpr" name="gdpr" required>
            <label for="gdpr">Jag godkänner att mina personuppgifter hanteras enligt integritetspolicyn.</label>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Skicka in</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>Kontaktuppgifter</h2>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Kontor</h3>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
            </svg>
            <p>Björneborgsgatan 36<br>854 60 Sundsvall</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Kontakt</h3>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
            <p><a href="tel:+46739823962">+46 73 982 39 62</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
              <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
            </svg>
            <p><a href="mailto:info@stenstadsmaklarna.se">info@stenstadsmaklarna.se</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Öppettider</h3>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
            <p>Måndag - Fredag: 09:00 - 17:00<br>Lördag - Söndag: Stängt</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="logo" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <div class="logo-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M3 21h18M5 21V9l7-6 7 6v12M9 21v-6h6v6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="logo-text" style="color: #fff;">Stenstadsmäklarna</span>
          </a>
          <p>Din lokala mäklare i Sundsvall. Vi hjälper dig genom hela bostadsaffären med personlig service och lokal expertis.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Tjänster</h4>
